      "template_id": "plotting",
      "title": "Plotting",
      "description": "2D and 3D plots with Maxima and gnuplot."
    }
  },
  "cells": [
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## 2D Plots",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "A simple sine wave over two full periods.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "plot2d(sin(x), [x, -2*%pi, 2*%pi])",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "Multiple functions on the same axes.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "plot2d([sin(x), cos(x), sin(x)+cos(x)], [x, -2*%pi, 2*%pi])",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## Customising Plots",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "Add a title, legend, and custom y-range.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "plot2d([sin(x), sin(2*x)], [x, 0, 2*%pi],\n  [legend, \"sin(x)\", \"sin(2x)\"],\n  [ylabel, \"y\"])",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## Parametric Plots",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "plot2d([parametric, cos(t), sin(t), [t, 0, 2*%pi]],\n  [nticks, 100])",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "A Lissajous figure.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "plot2d([parametric, sin(3*t), sin(4*t), [t, 0, 2*%pi]],\n  [nticks, 200])",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## 3D Surface Plots",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "A saddle surface.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "plot3d(x^2 - y^2, [x, -2, 2], [y, -2, 2])",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "A ripple pattern using sine.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "plot3d(sin(x^2 + y^2) / (x^2 + y^2 + 1),\n  [x, -4, 4], [y, -4, 4])",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## Plotting Computed Results",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "Compute a derivative and plot both the function and its derivative.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "f: x^3 - 3*x;\ndf: diff(f, x);\nplot2d([f, df], [x, -3, 3],\n  [legend, \"f(x)\", \"f'(x)\"])",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    }
  ]
}
